data.description: Nestled in the picturesque Holiday Village, this beautifully updated 4 bed, 3 full bath home offers the perfect blend of modern living and small-town charm. Step inside, and you'll discover an inviting floorplan with three bedrooms on the main level and a spacious fourth bedroom above the garage, complete with a private full bath. This home has been lovingly maintained and updated, featuring fresh carpet, new flooring, and a modern paint palette. There is also a whole-home solar panel system that is transferable. You can enjoy the gorgeous, wooded hilltop views from the covered front porch. The backyard is perfect for entertaining, with a spacious deck overlooking the woods and a private fire pit area. You're just minutes away from Holiday World Theme Park, beautiful lakes, parks, walking trails, local shopping, and dining. You also have access to the pool and recreation center of Holiday Village. Free Holiday World passes for the entire family included with HOA fees.
